smoog/README

Thomas Habets


Intro
-----
For now you will need a file called ~/.smug.cfg that contains three lines.
1) Your API key
2) Your email
3) your smugmug password

All scripts read the login info from there at the moment.

This will be improved upon.


Scripts
-------
albumSettings.py          Change album settings in bulk.
kwRename.py               Rename/remove a keyword everywhere it's used.
listAlbums.py             List albums in various output formats.

